  "keyFeatures": [
    "Modular NixOS configuration supporting multiple platforms (NixOS, macOS, WSL)",
    "Catppuccin theming across all applications and system components",
    "Declarative secrets management with sops-nix",
    "Multi-host support with easy host management via easy-hosts",
    "Home-manager integration for userspace configuration",
    "Secure boot support with lanzaboote",
    "Custom ISO image builder for system installation",
    "Justfile-based build and deployment automation"
  ],
